What's new in the latest update:
• Client statements - create, email and print a statement to any of your customers for a selected time period
• Stripe payments - let your clients pay invoices directly & online using common debit and credit cards
• Know if an invoice has been sent and viewed by your client
• Contact name is now displayed on an invoice
• Set up a Tax year start and your Statistics will match accordingly

The new iOS 11 caused many sleepless nights for our users and developers. We continuously try to fish out all bugs and maintain your user experience at the most convenient point. If you run into any inconsistencies or experience an issue please share your feedback with us - we are listening at support@billdu.com
